Report back to Managingway.
Coiningway's dream of opening a shopping station has been realized, but its available products are still rather limited.

After considering what else we might offer, we have collectively decided that memorabilia inscribed with your signature would be a most desirable item. You <hex:021A020203>are<hex:021A020103> the moon's leading celebrity, after all.
Those personalized memorabilia you provided us proved more popular than we anticipated. We sold them all just as soon as we stocked them!
Might you craft us some more? Needy Ways await.
We will, of course, provide adequate compensation for your time, labor, and use of your likeness. One of our Ways eagerly awaits you in Greatest Endsvale whenever you wish to begin production.
<blip> Please state your request.
Oooh! <hex:022903EB0203>, welcome, welcome! You've come to make some memorabilia for us, yes? It's an honor to assist you, <hex:02080EE905FF05>miss<hex:FF04>sir<hex:03>.
Anything you make is certain to sell like carrot cake, but our Ways would particularly love something with your name on it. And perhaps your face. Whatever you think is best!
Anything you make is certain to sell like carrot cake, but our Ways would particularly love something with your name on it. And perhaps your face. Whatever you think is best!
Anything you make is certain to sell like carrot cake, but our Ways would particularly love something with your name on it. And perhaps your face. Maybe even edible? I'll leave it to your discretion!
I've stocked this doing supporter with all sorts of materials, so don't worry about running out of supplies. Oh, I can't wait to see what you come up with!

Are you finished? Can I see?

Oh, how lovely! An item worthy of <hex:022903EB0203>'s name. I'll go and stock these in the shopping station straightaway─the others will riot when they see! Perhaps literally, now that I think about it. Oh dear... Er, Managingway should have your compensation waiting for you.

Thank you for your cooperation, <hex:022C0DFF07><hex:022903EB0203><hex:FF02> <hex:0203>. For all the help and hope you've given us, I am sure those mementos will be our shopping station's best seller.
Speaking of which, I must secure one for myself... Er, strictly for managerial purposes! Ahem.
